channel.title: Wow @ Alexa Rank
channel.description:
Hey, I can't believe this site only has an Alexa rank of 1,609,674... But its pretty easy to improve Alexa Rank, I am not sure how SMF is with SEO but you could work on the main site...
Also, People who are active on these forums should install Alexa'a toolbar... That improves it plenty...
For example, about two weeks ago I started a new site and it had like 9 million Alexa Rank at first, However I added Alexa's little rank banner (Which helps too) onto my site and visited my site daily with my Alexa toolbar and now its up to 4 Million.
I was just surprised :P Good luck.
